reviewText: Happy to find in DVD!
I loved these movies as a kid ! So glad to finally have them on DVDs !! They come in two DVDs. Two story's are on one disc and the one on the other. Got them for a great price and love them !
it's my daughter favorite movie and she grown women now it's still is.

I love these movies and was excited to get all three at once. I removed a star because the third movie is a disc all its own with a great picture for the menu screen. The first two movies are on one disc with a blank white menu screen. Just a bit of a let down there.
Great deal! Speedy delivery!!

My little girl loves these movies. And I love that I could get all three of them for her at once for her birthday. We had previously just been watching it via amazon prime so it's nice not to have to use the internet. My only gripe is that the color isn't as good as the online version.. Most of the time it's not an issue but sometimes it's like come on she has blonde hair -.- overall happy if they had an updated version its be perfect

Bought this product recently- have loved the films since I was a child. The storylines spanning Odette and Derek's beginning, to their adventures with Speed, Jean Bob, and Puffin, are great to watch. With lots of laughs, great music, and eccentric villains, this is a DVD worth buying.
